<inglise> - the cost of travel in a private car, based on second-class rail or coach travel, using the shortest route, supplements excluded; such costs are eligible on presentation of a declaration signed by the user specifying the dates of departure and return and the point of departure and the destination and an attestation from a rail or coach company indicating the cost of such a journey(2); expenditure incurred by the user of a private car on petrol, parking, road tolls and meals is not eligible, </inglise>
