<inglise> (c) accommodation and subsistence expenses, on the following conditions: </inglise>
<eesti> c) majutus- ja elamiskulud: </eesti>
<inglise> - up to a maximum amount per person per day (available from the Commission); this amount covers the cost of accommodation and of group meals taken in connection with implementation of the measure, on presentation of the invoices, </inglise>
