<inglise> - up to a maximum amount per person per meal (available from the Commission); where provision is made for some or all meals not to be taken together, </inglise>
<eesti> - komisjonilt saadava maksimumsumma piires inimese ja s&ouml;&ouml;gikorra kohta, kui on ette n&auml;htud, et m&otilde;ned v&otilde;i k&otilde;ik s&ouml;&ouml;gikorrad ei ole &uuml;hised, </eesti>
<inglise> - joint hotel bills are eligible only where they indicate the number of rooms, the names of the persons concerned and the number of nights; restaurant bills must specify the number of diners and a list of diners must be attached; </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;hised hotelliarved vastavad tingimustele ainult tingimusel, et nendel on m&auml;rgitud tubade arv, asjaomaste isikute nimed ning &ouml;&ouml;de arv; restoraniarvetel peab olema m&auml;rgitud einestajate arv ja neile peab olema lisatud einestajate loetelu; </eesti>
<inglise> (d) the cost of interpretation and translation, on the same conditions as personnel costs, up to maximum amounts (available from the Commission); </inglise>
