<inglise> (e) the fees of experts or speakers, up to a maximum amount (available from the Commission), on presentation of an invoice and proof of payment, provided that the persons concerned are not national, Community or international civil servants or members or employees of the organisation receiving the grant or an associated or affiliated organisation; </inglise>
<eesti> e) ekspertide ja loengupidajate tasud komisjonilt saadava maksimumsumma piires arve v&otilde;i makset&otilde;endi esitamisel tingimusel, et asjaomased isikud ei ole riigi, &uuml;henduse v&otilde;i rahvusvahelised avalikud teenistujad v&otilde;i toetust saava organisatsiooni v&otilde;i selle koost&ouml;&ouml;organisatsiooni v&otilde;i liikmesorganisatsiooni liikmed v&otilde;i t&ouml;&ouml;tajad; </eesti>
<inglise> (f) the hire of conference halls and equipment, on presentation of the invoice; </inglise>
<eesti> f) loenguruumide ja aparatuuri rent arve esitamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> (g) subcontracting, but only in those cases stipulated in the agreement; where the contract is for an amount of more than EUR 10000, the beneficiary must obtain three tenders, provide the Commission with proof that the subcontractor selected represents the best value and justify that choice where the tender selected is not the cheapest; the subcontractor is subject to the same rules as the beneficiary; </inglise>
<eesti> g) allt&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;tt ainult lepingus nimetatud juhtudel; kui leping on s&otilde;lmitud suuremale summale kui 10 000 eurot, peab toetuse saaja saama kolm pakkumist, t&otilde;endama komisjonile, et valitud allt&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;tja esindab parimat hinna ja kvaliteedi suhet ning p&otilde;hjendama oma valikut, kui valitud pakkumine ei olnud k&otilde;ige v&auml;iksem; allt&ouml;&ouml;v&otilde;tja suhtes kohaldatakse samu eeskirju kui toetuse saaja suhtes; </eesti>
<inglise> (h) the cost of publication and distribution and the cost of audio-visual productions, other than personnel costs, on presentation of the invoices; </inglise>
<eesti> h) avaldamis- ja levitamiskulud ning audiovisuaalse materjali tootmiskulud, v&auml;lja arvatud personalikulutused, arvete esitamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> (i) other costs arising from the requirements of the grant agreement (audits, specific evaluations of the measure, reports, translations, securities, etc.), on presentation of the invoices; </inglise>
<eesti> i) muud lepingu n&otilde;uetest tulenevad kulud (auditid, meetme erihindamised, aruanded, t&otilde;lked, tagatised jne) arvete esitamisel; </eesti>
<inglise> (j) a contingency reserve of a maximum of 5 % of the direct eligible costs; </inglise>
